formData.question: About Tarento
formData.answer: We are a Nordic-Indian company. Our headquarters is in Stockholm, Sweden. Our biggest unit and technology work is in Bangalore, India. Our consulting operations and data management expertise is in Helsinki, Finland.

formData.question: Technologies used in Tarento
formData.answer: Custom Java, .Net, PHP & RoR development, Sharepoint, Oracle Middleware, Adobe Flex/Flash, MS Dynamics, Enterprise Mobility, Testing and a few other technology areas.

formData.question: Projects handled by Tarento
formData.answer: Microsoft projects,Development of mobile and web-applications,SAP applications and QA

formData.question: Services provided by Tarento
formData.answer: Development, QA, Business Analyst, Project management, Resources to other companies.
